            %h2
              %b
                CONTINGENCY SEARCH 
            
          %p
            Ideal for early and mid-career professional positions. We research, source, screen and interview candidates within a 25-mile radius of the client office 
            and provide the client with a slate of 3-5 highly qualified candidates within 8 to 12 days. The client is invoiced a fee only after a placement is made. 
            
    .row
