        .columns.xlarge-8
          %h3
            %b  
              INTAKE AND DISCOVERY
          %p
            The hiring manager and key stakeholders provide insight and details to ensure the search consultant effectively market the opportunity.
          
    .row
      .box
        .columns.xlarge-4.text-center
          = image_tag 'ResearchCompany.png', :alt => "Research Company", :class => 'img55' 
        .columns.xlarge-8
          %h3
            %b
              RESEARCH COMPANIES 
          %p
            Using the latest databases and proprietary technology, Joynus identifies companies and candidates to headhunt within 25 miles of client location.
    
    .row
      .box
        .columns.xlarge-4.text-center
          = image_tag 'Marketing.png', :alt => "Marketing", :class => 'img55' 
        .columns.xlarge-8
          %h3
            %b
              MARKETING AND ADVERTISING
          %p  
            Joynus creates a unique script designed to attract candidates through cold calling and “headhunting” from the target market.  We place ads on social media to encourage networking.
            
    
    .row
      .box
        .columns.xlarge-4.text-center
          = image_tag 'CandidatePresentation.png', :alt => "Presentation", :class => 'img55' 
        .columns.xlarge-8
          %h3
            %b
              CANDIDATE PRESENTATION
          %p
            Within 8 - 12 business days from the intake call, Joynus will provide a slate of 3 - 5 highly qualified candidates and provide the client with a market review and analysis. 
            
    .row
      .box
        .columns.xlarge-4.text-center
          = image_tag 'Invoice.png', :alt => "Invoice", :class => 'img55' 
        .columns.xlarge-8
          %h3
